 href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/elektra/" rel="tag">Elektra</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/eva-johannson/" rel="tag">Eva Johannson</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/felicity-palmer/" rel="tag">Felicity Palmer</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/melanie-diener/" rel="tag">Melanie Diener</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/nikolaus-lenhoff/" rel="tag">Nikolaus Lenhoff</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-di-roma/" rel="tag">Opera di Roma</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica/" rel="tag">Opera lirica</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/raimund-bauer/" rel="tag">Raimund Bauer</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/richard-strauss/" rel="tag">Richard Strauss</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/stefan-soltesz/" rel="tag">Stefan Soltesz</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/wolfgang-schmidt/" rel="tag">Wolfgang Schmidt</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Alejandro Marco-Buhrmester, Derek Welton, Elektra, Eva Johannson, Felicity Palmer, Melanie Diener, Nikolaus Lenhoff, Opera di Roma, Opera lirica, Raimund Bauer, Richard Strauss, Stefan Soltesz, Wolfgang Schmidt"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/3979ab1c3d1e5c1cef46504929f6931b" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2008/04/Maurizi-129x200.jpg" width="65" height="100" alt="Massimiliano Maurizi" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Massimiliano Maurizi"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></